				\begin{document}$45^{\circ}$\end{document} roller and cage assembly increases the lateral and vertical stiffness. This translation stage is built to print from ChemCam, and was delivered by PI miCos, Germany, as a commercial product. See Maurice et al. (2012, Sect. 3.2.3) for details. Fig. 34
Supercam focus mechanism. (Credit: CNES/Alexandre Ollier, 2019)

